dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waukesha_Roads_2015.gdb. [The addressed street centerlines are a subset of Waukesha County's planimetric mapping product covering the entire county and were compiled at a scale of 1' = 100'. The accuracy standard used is National Map Accuracy for 1' = 100' scale mapping. ]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use. Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. [These centerline features were extracted from the DTM product and represent pavement centerline. The data was compiled as part of the County Orthophotography project.]
